Truck & Trailer Sales




Knight Truck and Trailer Sales

Knight Truck & Trailer Sales, LLC is a wholly owned subsidiary of Knight Transportation, one of the strongest trucking companies on the road today. Knight has been a dynamic force in transportation for over 20 years. We understand the demands on a company, especially the demands on equipment while on the road. We provide a quality sales experience and deliver exceptional equipment. In addition, we offer a diverse inventory of tractors, dry vans, and reefers. Our inventory of newer used equipment is located throughout the United States. All of our used equipment has been maintained within our industry leading maintenance program, and every truck and trailer meets or exceeds UTA (Used Truck Association) standards.

Knight Truck and Trailer Sales offer a wide range of financing options. Our finance team has the ability to review various options that are available for you, and find something that suits your needs. We have an established relationship with a number of lenders; affording us the opportunity to secure the best deal for you. Whether you are looking to buy your first truck, expand your fleet, or standardize your equipment, our team of professionals at Knight Truck and Trailer Sales is ready to meet your needs. The team consists of an experienced staff and together we have a combined 42 years with Knight. Let us help you succeed! Please give us a call or stop by one of our many locations.
To see our current inventory and get full details on purchase and finance options, visit our Web site at www.knighttrucksales.com.






Knight offers a variety of used trucks and trailers as well as a wide range of financing options.


