Knight Dedicated delivers more than just freight

Knight has the expertise and experience to handle your challenging transportation needs. We deliver freight with the highest levels of service while cutting transportation costs and optimizing your current operating environment. Knight is a highly efficient carrier and we apply that knowledge and expertise to examining your business and reducing your costs. 

Why Knight Dedicated?

Over 20 years of expertise running successful      dedicated operations, across the country
Guaranteed capacity-  access to      Knight’s nationwide network to handle your shipping spikes
Modern equipment: 2010 or newer tractors
We will source customized equipment to meet      your needs
Very low Driving Associate turnover means more consistent      service
Advanced operating systems and technology
All our equipment is paid for which means      building toward the future, not paying for the past

Knight’s Dedicated driving associates bring value to your network by delivering freight safely and on time. Choosing Knight Dedicated means your brand will be represented by one of the most respected carriers in the industry.   

Call 855-240-4584 or email to dedicatedservices@knighttrans.com for more information.





Knight has the expertise and experience to provide customized solutions.


