Knight Transportation Stock Sees Short Interest Decline 12.5%
The most recent short interest data has been released for the 12/15/2016 settlement date, which shows a 941,650 share decrease in total short interest for Knight Transportation Inc. , to 6,613,335, a decrease of 12.46% since 11/30/2016.

