Knight Transportation, Inc.

5601 West Buckeye Road 
Phoenix AZ 85043 United States
Phone: +1 602-___-____
Fax: +1 602-___-____
http://www.knighttrans.com





17
Managers




45
IT employees




$39.9MEST.
IT Budget




Knight Transportation is a motor shipping carrier, operating over 3,000 tractors and more than 8,500 trailers across the country. The company works out of 28 regional locations, and consists of Knight Transportation, Knight Refrigerated, Knight Brokerage, Knight Truck and Trailer… MoreKnight Transportation is a motor shipping carrier, operating over 3,000 tractors and more than 8,500 trailers across the country. The company works out of 28 regional locations, and consists of Knight Transportation, Knight Refrigerated, Knight Brokerage, Knight Truck and Trailer Sales, and Knight Intermodal.
The IT department at Knight Transportation oversees all IT strategy and operations for the enterprise and its subsidiaries from the AZ Headquarters.

Major divisions within the department are software, infrastructure and information security management. Within applications, a large focus is on… MoreThe IT department at Knight Transportation oversees all IT strategy and operations for the enterprise and its subsidiaries from the AZ Headquarters.

Major divisions within the department are software, infrastructure and information security management. Within applications, a large focus is on SAP-based supply chain management systems and coordinating with outsourcing contracts. Several aspects of the IT department are outsourced. Terion, Inc. maintains and develops truck and cargo tracking systems, and Spanlink is responsible for Cisco networking and telecommunication equipment.





