DELIVERING MORE
Better Tools of The Trade
At Knight Transportation, our goal isn’t just to get the job done, but to do it better every time. Here are some of the assets we utilize to accomplish that.

- More Capacity: Our consistent growth throughout the years has afforded us the opportunity to offer our customers the capacity they need to get their freight where it needs to go.

- More Quality Equipment: Our fleet is one of the newest and best maintained in the industry. Offering both customer and driver a more efficient means of transport.

- More Financial Options: At Knight we operate with one of the strongest balance sheets in the industry. This means that our abilities aren’t burdened by financial strain and our future is bright.

- More Efficiency: Environmental sustainability and fuel economy are at the forefront of the success of any carrier. That’s why we’re finding ways every day to work towards sustainable solutions for our company and the world we all share.








The Knight Difference
Compared to other top carriers.


